text: "Green Grass and High Tides" is a song by American Southern rock band Outlaws. A cover version appeared in the 2007 video game Rock Band as apart of the main game setlist. ==Trivia== Deanozord 5000 has the first on-disc FC of this song on Rock Band Xbox 360 on May 22, 2022 with a score of 763,575. UKOGmonkey has the first FC of this song on Rock Band 2 on February 8, 2009 with a score of 764,100. ==References== Category:1975 songs
title: Green Grass and High Tides
